data.description: *OFFER ACCEPTED 48-HR FIRST RIGHT* Discover the pinnacle of modern luxury in this exquisite open-plan modern farm house ranch nestled in the heart of Auburn, Indiana. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a wealth of custom features, this home redefines the art of comfortable living. With a prime location just 20 miles north of Fort Wayne and easy access to outdoor recreation, it offers a lifestyle that's both opulent and convenient. Culinary enthusiasts and home chefs will be captivated by the beautiful custom kitchen featuring pristine white quartz countertops. The kitchen effortlessly opens into the great room, creating a sense of space and unity. Cathedral ceilings and a gas fireplace create a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for gatherings with family and friends. Hard surface luxury vinyl plank floors grace the entertainment areas of this ranch, exuding both elegance and practicality, while providing low-maintenance living. The main bedroom is a sanctuary unto itself, with large walk-in closets featuring custom closet tamers. The en suite bathroom is a masterpiece, boasting a 5-foot ceramic walk-in shower and all the amenities you desire. A 2-car garage with an epoxied floor ensures that your vehicles and hobbies are well-cared for. The garage conveniently leads to a mudroom with custom lockers, keeping your home organized and clutter-free. From the large eat-in kitchen, step onto the covered patio and gaze upon the private fenced backyard, a serene haven for relaxation and entertaining. A substantial shed/greenhouse adds versatility to your outdoor space, allowing for gardening and storage options. Additionally, qualified buyers have the unique opportunity to assume a 2.99% interest rate mortgage with a 15% down payment, offering an enticing financial advantage. Located less than 20 minutes from Parkview Regional Medical Center, this property is a rare gem waiting to be claimed.
